{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "企图复活熔岩巨兽的魔兽\\n竟是佩雷曾经的主人阿克欧王。\\n打倒阿克欧王后不久，\\n面对裂缝中企图侵略世界的熔岩巨兽，\\n王子一行人向其发起决战！"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120065_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "嘎啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "真够顽强的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "嗯？\\n好像掉了什么。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "难道是……异界碎片？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "你知道那是什么吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我曾在书中读到过。\\n强大的魔兽会掉落异界碎片，\\n它蕴含着强大的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "据说碎片蕴含的强大魔力\\n足以扭曲空间。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "这玩意儿听起来真可怕啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "佩雷，\\n你怎么在发愣？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "我想起了过去的事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "回想起独眼魔兽还是王的时候，\\n与他共同度过的岁月。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "你说王……诶诶诶诶诶诶！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "难道那头魔兽的真身\\n是阿克欧王！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "没错……王和我一样，\\n为了封印熔岩巨兽被困在异界。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "王在充满黑暗魔力的空间\\n受到魔力影响，最终变成了魔兽。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "原来如此。王失去理智才做出了\\n试图复活熔岩巨兽的愚行……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "非也。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "王虽然变成了魔兽，\\n却还保有作为人类的意识。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "什么！？那他为什么\\n要复活仇敌熔岩巨兽！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "我不清楚……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "我只知道王变成魔兽后，\\n嘴里不停地在诅咒着什么。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "他诅咒的并不是熔岩巨兽，\\n而是看不见的某个存在。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "赛丽艾拉在故事里提到的\\n“哀怨之声”难道就是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "无论如何，没能阻止王\\n是我身为从者的失职。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "不……若要贯彻忠诚，\\n也许应该实现王之所愿吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "即使毁灭世界也在所不辞。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "佩雷，你说什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "请忘了我刚才的话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "咕噜嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这声音是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "这是异界空间的裂缝……\\n不，已经变成“出口”了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110255_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "赛丽艾拉",
            "context": "什么！？\\n我们来晚了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "往这里过来了啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "咳咳！咳咳！\\n呜呜……味道好难闻啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是熔岩巨兽正在接近的影响吧。\\n火山的魔力紊乱得厉害。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "只是接近就会这样吗！？\\n那要是它从裂缝中解放出来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那就闯进裂缝里，\\n在异界空间阻止它！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "不行！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "就这样闯入异界的话，\\n会撞上时空之壁粉身碎骨的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "难道我们只能在这里\\n眼睁睁地看着熔岩巨兽复活吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "人类想要跨越时空之壁，\\n需要借助超越此世常理之力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "超越此世常理之力……\\n啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我们能借助\\n那个异界碎片的力量吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "的确……\\n凭借碎片的力量也许行得通。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210057_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "佩雷",
            "context": "但是那家伙非常强大，\\n你们确定要与它一战吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "世界都面临危机了，\\n我们才不会退缩。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "无论对手有多强大，\\n我们都会战斗到底。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "即使拼上性命，\\n也在所不惜！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "而且除了我们之外，\\n也许还有其他人愿与其一战。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "得知世界面临危机，\\n从其它裂缝赶来相助的人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "熔岩巨兽",
            "context": "咕噜嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "出发吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20401_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}